snippet.title: Live Coding: Port scanners in C, Go, Python, Java
snippet.description:
Let's write some port scanners in a variety of languages including C, Go, Python, and Java. We'll start with simple TCP connect scans but we can also try to write a stealthy SYN only scanner using libpcap.
